[15/04/2019 19:35:19] <font color="#ffffff">Eso.</font>
[15/04/2019 19:35:22] <font color="#ffffff">Gracias, Julie.</font>
[15/04/2019 19:35:22] <font color="#ffffff">Un placer, Sabine.</font>
[15/04/2019 19:35:24] <font color="#ffffff">Hasta luego.</font>
